headline.main: Bjork, Jamieson Stay Ahead in Tshwane Open
headline.print_headline: Bjork, Jamieson Stay Ahead in Tshwane Open

lead_paragraph: Swedish rookie Alexander Bjork and Scott Jamieson of Scotland shared the lead again at the Tshwane Open on Saturday and will take a one-shot advantage into the final round.
